      <title>与 Nvidia 合作推动联发科股价创历史新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/nvidia-partnership-puts-mediatek-stock-on-course-for-record-high</link>
      <description><![CDATA[与英伟达公司加强合作，将投资者对联发科技 AI 增长潜力的乐观情绪推向了新的水平，使其股价有望在七个月内首次创下历史新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-10/nvidia-partnership-puts-mediatek-stock-on-course-for-record-high</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 Jan 2025 00:58:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
